#

Creamy Split Pea Soup

70 min
$10
250 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main

Tags:

SoupComfort FoodHealthy

Description

A hearty, creamy soup packed with nutrients and flavor, perfect for a cozy meal.

Ingredients

  • split peas: 1 cup
  • carrots: 2, diced
  • celery: 2 stalks, diced
  • onion: 1, chopped
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • potato: 1, peeled and diced
  • bay leaf: 1
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • fresh parsley: for garnish
